the keystore example password is "password"
And is hardcoded in the HttpsConfig file

To generate a new keystore, use the following command as example:

keytool -genkeypair -alias alias -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -keystore /path/src/main/resources/keystore-exmaple.p12 -storetype PKCS12 -validity 9999 -storepass password -keypass password -dname "CN=pt.pchouse, OU=reportapi, O=PCHOUSE, L=Lisboa, S=Lisboa, C=PT"